ABOUT US
</h1>

<p>
At TruPurpose Job Shop, we deliver a fresh and innovative service to Job Seekers and Employers/Recruiters across the South West of Nigeria. We work hard to unearth hidden and unadvertised jobs for Job seekers and deploy tailor made and cost effective recruitment solutions to employers. Our role is to work with employers and job seekers to facilitate a successful match.
</p>


<p>
We specialize in recruiting experienced and dedicated staff for schools, hospitals and other organizations and also deploy our robust database to identify the best and brightest candidates. Our recruitment team are dedicated to making the recruitment process simple and transparent. Once we have knowledge of your preferences, skillset and salary requirements, we will identify and keep you constantly updated with the most suitable opportunities throughout the South West of Nigeria.
</p>

<p>
We take into consideration each candidate’s expectations and career path. We try to find employment opportunities that correspond to a candidate’s profile and to provide them with interesting career opportunities, both in terms of the position and progression potential.
</p>

<P>
